{"tid":511973,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔出軌係世上最on9嘅事","createTime":"2017-12-28T04:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T00:42:27.000Z","uid":54581,"like":3,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"faa70d183d00d9d834a642f0e307b4740a807381","tid":511973,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:22:07.000Z","msg":"反正你十幾廿幾歲人 肯定拍唔長拖<br />\n<br />\n最後都會散 咁你偷唔偷食都無所謂啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且你唔出去玩 另一半都好有可能ONS<br />\n（題外話 講下我經歷 <br />\n有條女 幾靚女既HD妹 出黎同我扑完中出完 第二朝就po 同另外個男仔嘅合照上ig 個時先知條仔追左佢好耐 條女接受左佢表白仲同我出黎玩一晚先po ig<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二條女就係番上去做野時識 個位女同事有個拍左好多年拖既男友 點個佢又叫我落club又撩我上佢屋企吹水 仲夠膽死傾傾下走去沖涼<br />\n結果我當然晚晚狂歡啦 佢條仔就慘囉<br />\n<br />\n第三條女係我大學時期既組女, 個樣好純好純 仲要係讀得書dean list 個隻<br />\n有次通宵K 大家吹下水 玩下酒game 佢就自爆試過ONS  <br />\n<br />\n我個下真係O撚左咀 黎尾我見到兩個獸父夾左佢入廁所 玩左咩我就唔知lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講左咁多野 都係想講 係女/仔都會出軌 你有道德底線係你傻豬 唔好expect 人都有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁你唔咁做 咪蝕撚左？"},{"pid":"1ede1252bd43ebd0a3a2ed541adea91babd4d8f3","tid":511973,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e8024521d9a7db90931f3d638296cafe9c2a17","tid":511973,"uid":83094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:51:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08e3240a301bb8e5f7b4a893760951ffec3e70f5","tid":511973,"uid":56240,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:52:16.000Z","msg":"樓主係火車？"},{"pid":"4fc20c1d1254e2237125a355d27b9a3715e7a414","tid":511973,"uid":120179,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:57:44.000Z","msg":"認同樓主～<br />\n正所謂人一世物一世，點都想試下出軌嘅感覺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似你老母訓緊係我隔離咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d323578e99ef6e1ca1d24b0891afacaa4c76ade","tid":511973,"uid":88888,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T05:03:59.000Z","msg":"你老母生你出黎就真係世上最on9嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51cbe881477bf8e8ab26a72b73ba9350ec5a8b36","tid":511973,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T05:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c4266f904b0f439ce5a87a5e236ec3c568e69f","tid":511973,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23062ee5e95c5f27195875182314635967a61ed","tid":511973,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T09:23:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"74f2acf6c812b426c927ececb65fad9f5a57b202","tid":511973,"uid":49918,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T09:29:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ad1d947394c89f7c8676a8c3374463eea9d7a8f","tid":511973,"uid":19527,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T09:32:12.000Z","msg":"返上去姐係邊到？蒙主寵召？"},{"pid":"e5d873f4552f42c83aefed553a731590360a7e63","tid":511973,"uid":82872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T11:35:38.000Z","msg":"呢d咪世界第一on9囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9970d7abb62af4e70ffb2bc0a4be5adb5c1024da","tid":511973,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T19:39:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返上去姐係邊到？蒙主寵召？</blockquote><br />\n大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb0fe7fb34bfa5eb3e